{"type":"message","id":"b47e978f","parentId":"ba72df03","timestamp":"2026-04-16T06:47:15.854Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_r9PNPG8Gfb1NmOjfjLpmuZR0|fc_0beebb82725bec5a0169e085f301a48191a575a192802e6f71","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776322035851}}
