{"type":"message","id":"f7413ce6","parentId":"d433f545","timestamp":"2026-04-16T07:05:51.238Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-16 07:05 UTC] 1. The Correct Docling Endpoints\nBased on the docling-serve specification for the :latest image, your agent should use the following endpoints to process your Gemini logs:\n\nPrimary File Conversion: http://docling:5001/v1alpha/convert/file (Expects a multipart/form-data POST request).\n\nDocumentation Discovery: http://docling:5001/docs (Swagger UI) or http://docling:5001/openapi.json.\n\nAlternative Conversion Path: Some versions use http://docling:5001/v1/convert/file."}],"timestamp":1776323151224}}
