{"type":"message","id":"5d800f7e","parentId":"a4f54bab","timestamp":"2026-04-16T07:10:36.691Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_75dX03ryGnsahCFs3tvsa0PQ|fc_0beebb82725bec5a0169e08b6792888191af6cabad0a1c5a93","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP 200\n---HEAD---\n{\"document\":{\"filename\":\"MyActivity.html\",\"md_content\":\"### 1. The Google Takeout Extraction SOP\\n\\n1. **Access the Portal** : Navigate to [takeout.google.com](https://takeout.google.com/) . Ensure you are logged into the account containing your Project Apollo research.\\n2. **Clear the Deck** : Click **\\\"Deselect all\\\"** at the top of the list to avoid downloading gigabytes of unnecessary data.\\n3. **The \\\"Gems\\\" Layer** : Scroll down and check the box for **\\\"Gemini\\\"** . This exports your custom Gemini \\\"Gems\\\" configurations.\\n4. **The \\\"History\\\" Layer (Critical Step)** :\\n    - Scroll down to **\\\"My Activity\\\"** and check the box.\\n    - Click the button labeled **\\\"All activity data included\\\"** .\\n    - In the pop-up, click **\\\"Deselect all\\\"** , then scroll down and check **ONLY \\\"Gemini Apps\\\"** . Click **\\\"OK\\\"** .\\n5. **Finalize Export** :\\n    - Scroll to the bottom and click **\\\"Next step\\\"** .\\n    - **Delivery Method** : Choose \\\"Send download link via email\\\".\\n    - **File Type** : Select **.zip** for maximum compatibility with your local workstation.\\n    - Click **\\\"Create export\\\"** .\\n\\n### 2. Processing the Payload for Apollo\\n\\nOnce your export arrives (usual\n---SIZE---\n6945366 /tmp/tmp.VYvnkHjS9r\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tidy-shell","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"HTTP 200\n---HEAD---\n{\"document\":{\"filename\":\"MyActivity.html\",\"md_content\":\"### 1. The Google Takeout Extraction SOP\\n\\n1. **Access the Portal** : Navigate to [takeout.google.com](https://takeout.google.com/) . Ensure you are logged into the account containing your Project Apollo research.\\n2. **Clear the Deck** : Click **\\\"Deselect all\\\"** at the top of the list to avoid downloading gigabytes of unnecessary data.\\n3. **The \\\"Gems\\\" Layer** : Scroll down and check the box for **\\\"Gemini\\\"** . This exports your custom Gemini \\\"Gems\\\" configurations.\\n4. **The \\\"History\\\" Layer (Critical Step)** :\\n    - Scroll down to **\\\"My Activity\\\"** and check the box.\\n    - Click the button labeled **\\\"All activity data included\\\"** .\\n    - In the pop-up, click **\\\"Deselect all\\\"** , then scroll down and check **ONLY \\\"Gemini Apps\\\"** . Click **\\\"OK\\\"** .\\n5. **Finalize Export** :\\n    - Scroll to the bottom and click **\\\"Next step\\\"** .\\n    - **Delivery Method** : Choose \\\"Send download link via email\\\".\\n    - **File Type** : Select **.zip** for maximum compatibility with your local workstation.\\n    - Click **\\\"Create export\\\"** .\\n\\n### 2. Processing the Payload for Apollo\\n\\nOnce your export arrives (usual\n---SIZE---\n6945366 /tmp/tmp.VYvnkHjS9r\n","name":"tmp=$(mktemp) &&"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776323436684}}
